00:12:49.460 --> 00:12:50.420
Nos bons e maus momentos.

00:12:52.420 --> 00:12:53.420
Eu brindarei a ti.

00:12:53.420 --> 00:12:54.380
Fengxia,

00:12:55.380 --> 00:12:56.340
Amo-te.

00:13:00.660 --> 00:13:01.620
Anda lá.

00:13:05.700 --> 00:13:06.820
Então, escolheu

00:13:07.520 --> 00:13:08.380
